This project is a hands-on Azure home lab designed to simulate a Security Operations Center (SOC) environment.

The lab demonstrates:
- Azure Virtual Network (VNet) and subnet design
- Network Security Group (NSG) rules for inbound/outbound traffic control
-Flow logging for networks traffic visibility
-Least priviledge access and SOC-style monitoring

It is intended for learning, portfolio showcase, and demonstrating foundational cloud security skills to recruiters or SOC teams.
